[
    {
        "text": "August 7, 2020    My First Encounter With Orangutans", 
        "line": 0, 
        "range": [
            1, 
            52
        ], 
        "entities": []
    }, 
    {
        "text": "", 
        "line": 1, 
        "range": [], 
        "entities": []
    }, 
    {
        "text": "My first encounter with Orangutans in bukit lawang. Seeing animals in their real habitat living wild and free without cages or fences trapping them is a vary experience compares to a zoo visit. There\u2019s a different sensation when you meet them face to face. The biggest concern when we try to approach them wildly is the possibility of not seeing them. The fact that their natural instinct to human being, and the fact that they scatter deep inside the jungle.", 
        "line": 2, 
        "range": [
            54, 
            514
        ], 
        "entities": [
            {
                "type": "LOC_NAME", 
                "span": [
                    92, 
                    104
                ], 
                "name": "bukit lawang"
            }, 
            {
                "type": "LOC_NOM", 
                "span": [
                    135, 
                    142
                ], 
                "name": "habitat"
            }, 
            {
                "type": "FAC_NOM", 
                "span": [
                    172, 
                    177
                ], 
                "name": "cages"
            }, 
            {
                "type": "FAC_NOM", 
                "span": [
                    181, 
                    187
                ], 
                "name": "fences"
            }, 
            {
                "type": "FAC_NOM", 
                "span": [
                    237, 
                    240
                ], 
                "name": "zoo"
            }, 
            {
                "type": "LOC_NOM", 
                "span": [
                    506, 
                    512
                ], 
                "name": "jungle"
            }
        ]
    }, 
    {
        "text": "", 
        "line": 3, 
        "range": [], 
        "entities": []
    }, 
    {
        "text": "I had no intention at all to visit even the best zoo in the world. I prefer seeing wild animals in their real habitat. My first encounter with an exotic animal was Komodo Dragon in Komodo National Park. It was such an amazing experience for me. Not all efforts that I tried were successful. I had to bite my fingers due to a disappointment for not seeing One-Horned Rhino in Ujung Kulon National Park.", 
        "line": 4, 
        "range": [
            516, 
            916
        ], 
        "entities": [
            {
                "type": "FAC_NOM", 
                "span": [
                    564, 
                    567
                ], 
                "name": "zoo"
            }, 
            {
                "type": "LOC_NOM", 
                "span": [
                    625, 
                    632
                ], 
                "name": "habitat"
            }, 
            {
                "type": "FAC_NAME", 
                "span": [
                    696, 
                    716
                ], 
                "name": "Komodo National Park"
            }, 
            {
                "type": "FAC_NAME", 
                "span": [
                    890, 
                    915
                ], 
                "name": "Ujung Kulon National Park"
            }
        ]
    }, 
    {
        "text": "", 
        "line": 5, 
        "range": [], 
        "entities": []
    }, 
    {
        "text": "My next mission to accomplish was to \u201chunt\u201d down an amazing creature, which is said close and similar enough to mankind, the great apes, Orang utans. In my language, Malay or Bahasa, Orang means person/man and Utan/Hutan means forest, so combined it means jungle of forest person. Orang utans settles for ages in the jungle of Sumatera and Borneo.", 
        "line": 6, 
        "range": [
            918, 
            1268
        ], 
        "entities": [
            {
                "type": "LOC_NOM", 
                "span": [
                    1145, 
