    }, 
    {
        "text": "", 
        "line": 7, 
        "range": [], 
        "entities": []
    }, 
    {
        "text": "Heading to Bukit Lawang for the Orang Utans.", 
        "line": 8, 
        "range": [
            1270, 
            1313
        ], 
        "entities": [
            {
                "type": "LOC_NAME", 
                "span": [
                    1278, 
                    1290
                ], 
                "name": "Bukit Lawang"
            }
        ]
    }, 
    {
        "text": "", 
        "line": 9, 
        "range": [], 
        "entities": []
    }, 
    {
        "text": "It was actually a bit unplanned, my visit to Bukit Lawang. I had to bound to Medan for some paperwork where I met my old friend and surf to his place in Binjai, about an hour from Medan. The plan suddenly popped up. His place is not far from Bukit Lawang. about two hours ride passing crappy road, with both sides planted with palm oil trees, not a delightful sight.", 
        "line": 10, 
        "range": [
            1315, 
            1680
        ], 
        "entities": [
            {
                "type": "LOC_NAME", 
                "span": [
                    1358, 
                    1370
                ], 
                "name": "Bukit Lawang"
            }, 
            {
                "type": "LOC_NAME", 
                "span": [
                    1390, 
                    1395
                ], 
                "name": "Medan"
            }, 
            {
                "type": "FAC_NOM", 
                "span": [
                    1457, 
                    1462
                ], 
                "name": "place"
            }, 
            {
                "type": "LOC_NAME", 
                "span": [
                    1466, 
                    1472
                ], 
                "name": "Binjai"
            }, 
            {
                "type": "LOC_NAME", 
                "span": [
                    1493, 
