                ], 
                "name": "bus stop"
            }
        ]
    }, 
    {
        "text": "Head to the bus stop at the airport and search for \u201cALS\u201d bus that goes to Binjai (destination name). This bus cost you Rp 40.000. Next, after the bus stops in Binjai, take a rickshaw (Rp 10.000) to an area called Tanah Lapang where you can get minivan (Rp 20,000) to Bukit Lawang. Just mention that you\u2019re looking for minivan to Bukit Lawang. The journey slightly takes around 4-5 hours in total", 
