    }, 
    {
        "text": "", 
        "line": 40, 
        "range": [], 
        "entities": []
    }, 
    {
        "text": "Guide information Bukit Lawang", 
        "line": 41, 
        "range": [
            5137, 
            5166
        ], 
        "entities": []
    }, 
    {
        "text": "", 
        "line": 42, 
        "range": [], 
        "entities": []
    }, 
    {
        "text": "Taking a guide is a must for your own safety. The path is not clear, no direction, you might get lost in the middle of jungle. Hiring a guide or taking a tour here is very pricey. There\u2019s a guide association with fix rate. Normally the accommodation offers a day tour to see Orang utans.", 
        "line": 43, 
        "range": [
            5168, 
            5456
        ], 
        "entities": [
            {
                "type": "LINE_NOM", 
                "span": [
                    5191, 
                    5195
                ], 
                "name": "path"
            }, 
            {
                "type": "LOC_NOM", 
                "span": [
                    5260, 
                    5266
                ], 
                "name": "jungle"
            }, 
            {
                "type": "FAC_NOM", 
                "span": [
                    5377, 
                    5390
                ], 
                "name": "accommodation"
            }
        ]
    }, 
    {
        "text": "", 
        "line": 44, 
        "range": [], 
        "entities": []
    }, 
    {
        "text": "Some recommended guide: Dede Pinem +62821 6833 7066 or +62813 7047 0414, Robet Tuex  +62812 6099 8236. For Indonesian/local expect to pay around Rp 350.000/person. for foreigners expect to pay $50-$100 depends on the trekking type you take.", 
        "line": 45, 
        "range": [
            5458, 
            5697
        ], 
        "entities": []
    }, 
    {
        "text": "", 
        "line": 46, 
        "range": [], 
        "entities": []
    }, 
    {
        "text": "There\u2019s a controversy about feeding Orang utans. Some guides are strict with the rules, they\u2019re actually not allowed to feed them. But some guides still feed them to lure the Orang utans closer in order to entertain the guest.", 
        "line": 47, 
        "range": [
            5699, 
            5928
        ], 
        "entities": []
    }, 
    {
        "text": "", 
        "line": 48, 
        "range": [], 
        "entities": []
    }, 
    {
        "text": "Just a Small Opinion of Mine", 
        "line": 49, 
        "range": [
            5930, 
            5957
        ], 
        "entities": []
    }, 
    {
        "text": "", 
        "line": 50, 
        "range": [], 
        "entities": []
    }, 
    {
        "text": "To be honest, I was a bit shocked with the condition of Bukit Lawang. As far as I know, Bukit Lawang is a popular destination especially for foreigners so I expected that place as a part of national park will be more organized. I found out the facilities are under-supervised.", 
        "line": 51, 
        "range": [
            5959, 
            6234
        ], 
        "entities": [
            {
                "type": "LOC_NAME", 
                "span": [
                    5986, 
                    5998
                ], 
                "name": "Bukit Lawang"
            }, 
            {
                "type": "LOC_NAME", 
                "span": [
                    6018, 
                    6030
                ], 
                "name": "Bukit Lawang"
            }, 
            {
                "type": "LOC_NOM", 
                "span": [
                    6101, 
                    6106
                ], 
                "name": "place"
            }, 
            {
                "type": "FAC_NOM", 
                "span": [
                    6120, 
                    6133
                ], 
                "name": "national park"
            }, 
            {
                "type": "FAC_NOM", 
                "span": [
                    6174, 
                    6184
                ], 
                "name": "facilities"
            }
        ]
    }, 
    {
        "text": "", 
        "line": 52, 
        "range": [], 
        "entities": []
    }, 
    {
        "text": "The tourist information doesn\u2019t provide well information to the guest. I didn\u2019t know who to talk to because it\u2019s hard for me to find which one is the officer. There previous guy told me to buy entrance ticket and it\u2019s going to be checked when we arrived at the check point. I didn\u2019t see a proper check point and a proper officer who check our tickets.", 
        "line": 53, 
        "range": [
            6236, 
            6596
        ], 
        "entities": [
            {
                "type": "FAC_NOM", 
                "span": [
                    6469, 
                    6480
                ], 
                "name": "check point"
            }, 
            {
                "type": "FAC_NOM", 
                "span": [
                    6504, 
                    6515
                ], 
                "name": "check point"
            }
        ]
    }, 
    {
        "text": "", 
        "line": 54, 
        "range": [], 
        "entities": []
    }, 
    {
        "text": "There\u2019re just a bunch of people in the hut playing cards. That\u2019s a bit funny. I think the private runs their own business, no synergy among the official body from the national park. I could still accept this kind of condition if it\u2019s in different place which is not popular and still underdeveloped, not for Bukit Lawang. The potential is so big here, but it\u2019s not well-maintained.", 
        "line": 55, 
        "range": [
            6598, 
            6986
        ], 
        "entities": [
            {
                "type": "FAC_NOM", 
                "span": [
                    6600, 
                    6603
                ], 
                "name": "hut"
            }, 
            {
                "type": "FAC_NOM", 
                "span": [
                    6728, 
                    6741
                ], 
                "name": "national park"
            }, 
            {
                "type": "LOC_NOM", 
                "span": [
                    6808, 
                    6813
                ], 
                "name": "place"
